      "content": "That \"natural progression\" line is good, but it feels a little thin if they dig into the specific language of the bill. If they pull up the old transcript where the candidate explicitly called these exact tax provisions \"poisonous,\" what's the play? We can't just pretend they didn't say those words. How do we frame that specific hypocrisy so the sentiment score stays in the green?",
